INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (54, 21, '<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">11月份</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span class="15" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">西服</span></a></span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">产量状况</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">2011年11月份，我国生产<strong>西服套装</strong>5096.75&nbsp;万件，同比下降2.44&nbsp;%。中商情报网数据显示:2011年1-11月，全国</span><strong><span><a href="http://www.askci.com/reports/2011/07/2014533133184.shtml"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">西服套装</span></a></span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">的产量达5.37亿件，同比增长11.15&nbsp;%。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">从各省市的产量来看，2011年前11个月，我国</span><strong><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,255); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">西服套装</span></a></span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">生产的前三省市是江苏、广东和浙江</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span class="15" style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">（</span><span class="15" style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">www.bjqingyang.com</span><span class="15" style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">）</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">，分别占总产量的24.27%、14.39%和10.62%。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">男士西服销量大幅上扬</span></a></span></h2>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 30pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">整个<strong>男装</strong>市场都受到纤细造型风靡的推动</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">（</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">www.bjqingyang.com</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">）</span></a></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">，<strong>西服</strong>销量成大幅上升。根据NPD集团的调查