 background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">金奖1名、银奖2名、铜奖3名</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">最具市场潜力奖、最佳创意奖、最具网络人气奖各一名</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">优秀奖5名</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">(凡是获奖选手都可获得组委会颁发的荣誉证书一份，金银铜奖获奖者可到展会现场与企业进行作品展示讲解)</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial i