-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">4.服装设计爱好者</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">本届赛事将于2013年4月15日正式启动，报名截止时间为5月25日，历时1个多月，现面向国内外专业职业装设计师(包括港、澳、台地区)、全国职业装设计人员(包括在职或非在职)、全国各大服装院校师生和服装设计爱好者等征选设计作品。希冀各选手做好准备，踊跃参赛。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">庆洋制衣网（www.bjqingyang.com）：有兴趣的朋友可以进入相应网站报名，预祝此次职业装博览会成功！</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', '');
