; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102171832_1.jpg'')" height="497" alt="羽绒服定制" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY53360DF-3GG.jpg" width="340" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服价格昂贵</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">顾客只看不买</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">今年冬装市场中，羽绒服的价格</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">可为是一路攀升的让人有点难以接受，好多顾客都虽是冲着购买的目标去挑选羽绒服</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">但购买的欲望却被价格的昂贵给打消了，所以造成了好多商场的顾客是只看不买。</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">订做或翻新备受瞩目</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">订做</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服的顾客不少，定做一件短款羽绒服价位在<font face="Times New Roman">300</font><font face="宋体">多元，长款在</font><font face="Times New Roman">400</font><font face="宋体">元左右。而自带旧羽绒服翻新的则视顾客选择面料不同而价格有所不同，一般</font><font face="Times New Roman">200</font><font face="宋体">元左右就能搞定。一些年轻顾客把自己喜欢的羽绒服图片拿到店里，款式、配件不复杂，我们都能照着做。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="width: 492px; cursor: pointer; height: 485px" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120102/208_120102171913_1.jpg'')" height="750" alt="羽绒服订做" src="/uploads/allimg/c130507/13CY533E33Z-41118.jpg" width="750" border="0" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', '');
