o-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yurongfubaoyang/11160.html"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 10pt; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''" class="15">羽绒服洗涤三忌</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''" class="15">&nbsp;</span></a></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yurongfubaoyang/16351.html"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 10pt; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''" class="15">白色羽绒服怎么洗</span></a></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span><a href="http://www.bjqingyang.com/yurongfu/"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 10pt; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''" class="15">北京羽绒服定做,羽绒服批发厂家,羽绒服加工厂,外贸羽绒服订单-庆洋羽绒服</span></a></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">详情咨询</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">400-600-1689&nbsp;&nbsp;QQ：800020307</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>', '', '', '')