r-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">4</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">、防水：主要针对专业型羽绒服，在酷寒环境下直接外穿的，羽绒服的面料要直接代替冲锋衣使用。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点一</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">时装化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">时装化将成为羽绒服新款图片的主流。生活条件越好，人们对美的追求就越高。近年来天气越来越暖，各种活动场所的环境也越来越舒适，御寒已不再是人们穿羽绒服的惟一目的。从生产技术上，羽绒服已经可以做到既轻薄又保暖。所以，在人们越来越讲究美体、线条的今天，羽绒服独特的质感又是其它服装所无法相比的。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点四</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">个性化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">个性特色鲜明的新款羽绒服图片将标新立异。注重表现个性，是新时代消费者在着装方面的一大特点，羽绒服也不例外。如情侣装、母子装羽绒服将会备受消费者的青睐。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点二</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">休闲化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">在着装上，人们将更加讲究丰富多彩和随意性。休闲服装洒脱、舒适、随意、放松，体现人们享受美好生活的乐观与惬意。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点三</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">运动化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><sp