color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (226, 20, '内容导读：羽绒服有内搭和外穿之分，知名品牌都在羽绒服款式及功能上每年都有创新，现在很多消费者会选择内穿型羽绒服，那么内穿型羽绒服和外穿型羽绒服在结构和功能上有什么区别呢？这些疑问就有专业的羽绒服生产厂家来告诉大家吧.</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">内穿型羽绒服款式及特点介绍&mdash;&mdash;【羽绒服面料专题】</span></h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服有内搭和外穿之分，知名品牌都在羽绒服款式及功能上每年都有创新，现在很多消费者会选择内穿型羽绒服，那么内穿型羽绒服和外穿型羽绒服在结构和功能上有什么区别呢？</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">这些疑问就有专业的<strong></strong>家来告诉大家吧.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">内穿型羽绒服款式及特点介绍</span></span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1、修身合体&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">这一点非常重要。既然定位于内穿，那就意味着外面还有一层衣物，这层衣物可能是防风的，也可能是防水的，也有可能是防止刮蹭的。因为有了这一层，使很多版型设计师都很犯难，设计不好会造成使用人员活动受限或者穿着不舒适。所以，为了安全起见，大多能见到的内穿型羽绒服都广泛采用了衬衫袖式的设计，就是袖肥加大，袖笼加深，不仅不美观，穿着起来腋下和两臂内侧总感觉有一层多余的东西存在，远距离徒步的时候更是感觉明显。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2、活动度大&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">这个问题和上面的问题是两码事。有同学可能不理解，袖子过肥也可能影响活动度，特别是抬臂的动作；过瘦自然就不用说了，前后活动都会受到束缚。解决这个问题是要看版师的功力了，关键是要有合理的结构和剪裁安排，有时候连一个简单的包边都会影响到舒适度。而且，多数超薄面料的伸缩性也都不太好，面料剪裁的经纬度走向对活动舒适性的影响也非常大。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3、高度透气&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">透气不透气，面料是关键。很多薄型材料为了能达到防绒目的，广泛采用增加涂层的方法来实现，或者是直接采用外加一层不透气的防绒内胆来实现。这样做的缺点显而易见，活动量一大，内层衣物部分或全部湿透，更无舒适度可言。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4、薄厚适度&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">内穿型的羽绒服不同于外穿型的羽绒服，外穿型的户外羽绒服主要在严寒地区使用，大都尽量追求蓬松效果和保暖度，并在设计上配以巨大的帽兜。内穿型的一般都是在寒冷地区作为中层保暖层来使用的，有或无帽兜，可以取代较重而保暖性较差的抓绒类服装。如果过厚会造成过热，大量出汗，而且会造成冲锋衣内层结霜，甚至会打湿羽绒服影响保温效果；过薄又起不到应有的保温效果。适度的薄厚对活动度的影响也很大，特别是腋下、手臂内侧和身体外侧部位。所以，内穿型的羽绒服薄厚适度也是相当重要的。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5、超轻便携&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">户外运动天气变化无常，内穿的羽绒服被很多玩家当成为一件备用品携带的，也就是说不一定总穿在身上。这就要求羽绒服具有一定的超轻型能和可收纳性，其好处不言而喻。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">6、高效防绒&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">面料和羽绒品质的影响大家都比较了解了，这里不多说。缝纫本身的影响其实也很大。针距过大和针眼过大是普遍存在的问题，这个大家可以留心一下。内穿的羽绒服一旦漏绒，哪怕是很细小的绒丝钻入内衣都会造成皮肤发痒，造成出汗的时候产生不适感。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">当然，还有很多因素可以谈，只是对于内穿来说针对性不很强，这里就不罗嗦了。有兴趣的同学可以注意一下市场上各种</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(62,62,62); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">品牌</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">的内穿型羽绒服，有多少能满足以上的几点要求。（来源：）</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (227, 20, '内容导读：近几年羽绒服面料几个一路高歌，据市场调研发现，得知羽绒服面料厂家热销的几款羽绒服面料，接下就一一介绍热销羽绒服面料的种类及特点。庆洋羽绒服订做厂家呈上。</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">热销羽绒服面料种类及特点介绍&mdash;&mdash;【羽绒服面料】</span></h1>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">近几年<strong></strong>面料几个一路高歌，据市场调研发现，得知羽绒服面料厂家热销的几款羽绒服面料，接下就一一介绍热销<strong></strong>的种类及特点。庆洋<strong></strong>呈上。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">热销羽绒服面料种类介绍</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">1、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">高密尼丝纺：如300T、310T消光尼丝纺，原料规格40D*40D，主要是斜纹类，风格多为菱形格，风格比较单一。在后整理上也多做三防处理，色调以淡色为主，门幅160CM，该羽绒服面料批发市场参考价在5.80-6.30元/米之间。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">2、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">高密春亚纺：主要是290T、300T消光春亚纺，原料规格50D*50D&nbsp;DTY，主要有平纹、斜纹两种组织</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">需求多样化，有格子、横条、峰巢、满天星等。在后整理加工上也丰富多样，防水、防污、防紫外线等。门幅160CM，该羽绒服面料批发市场参考价在3.5-4.1元/米之间。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">3、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">高密涤塔夫：原料50D*50D&nbsp;FDY，以300T为主，多是粗斜纹组织。超细旦涤塔夫面料是今秋盛泽市场出现的新品种，主要与后整理复合、涂层连起来进行深加工。最近在市场上销售活跃，亮点不断，同时，该羽绒服面料批发市场价格也在8.10元/米上下。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">热销羽绒服面料特点介绍</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">一是高密度。我们可以看出，不论是尼丝纺、春亚纺还是涤塔夫都强调高密度。分析其原因：一方面宜于保温;二来方便后道整理进行深加工。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">二是色彩淡而亮。据市场经营户反映，今年羽绒服厂商十分的偏爱淡彩色，乳白、粉红、浅绿等色彩较为突出。分析原因，主要是时代进步，人们的生活观也随之改变，这几种颜色不论老少，成衣在身，都会显得活力四射，魅力无穷。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">三是功能化。以上这些羽绒服面料除了做常规的防水、防油、防紫外线处理外，还兼有防静电、吸湿排汗等功能，加之环保印染，让人穿着非常舒适，功能更胜一筹。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">更多羽绒服面料动态资讯，尽请关注</span><span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">咨询专题或登录雅迪儿制衣官网</span><span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">进行搜索。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (228, 20, '内容导读：羽绒服的选购主要根据使用者的需要，首先是选择一件适合自己的羽绒服，然后是选择一件品质好的羽绒服。羽绒服根据环境的不同，要选择合适功能的羽绒服，比如，滑雪的，有滑雪羽绒服，登山的有登山羽绒服。如何挑选羽绒服装？羽绒服选购有哪些技巧？小编来为你一一解答。</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">如何挑选羽绒服装&nbsp;羽绒服选购有哪些技巧&mdash;&mdash;【羽绒服辨别知识】</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">的选购主要根据使用者的需要，首先是选择一件适合自己的羽绒服，然后是选择一件品质好的羽绒服。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服根据环境的不同，要选择合适功能的羽绒服，比如，滑雪的，有滑雪羽绒服，登山的有登山羽绒服。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">如何挑选羽绒服装？<strong></strong>有哪些技巧？小编来为你一一解答。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120614/1_120614161804_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/c130513/13D43595422N0-15164.jpg" width="310" height="310" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">严寒地带作业或旅游：最好是长款羽绒服、面料较耐磨、有较多的口袋放置随身物品，最好帽沿有毛皮防风。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">如普通登山考察者，除了关注羽绒服的保暖性以，更应考虑服装的通透性，因在运动中可能会大量出汗，如不能及时排出，可能导致严重后果。目前市场流行的所谓&ldquo;冲锋衣&rdquo;就是为了适应这种需求应运而生的。因此面料要求防水防风透气。也可以使用内胆式羽绒服在外层加冲锋衣。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">长途旅行：一般在路上时间较长，所经过的环境也有很大的差异，也就是说可能会出现在某些地方需要羽绒服御寒而某些地方可能穿T恤的情况。因此，对羽绒服的要求是体积小、重量轻，可以在不需要的时候压缩放在背包很小的一个角落里。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">滑雪：</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">适合滑雪用的羽绒服应该是透气效果好，不能太厚，贴身设计防止风阻效应，面料耐磨强度高。&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服选购有哪些技巧</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">：</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一看：看有无注册商标、产品使用说明及相关内容是否标注齐全，如厂名、厂址、面料里料的成份含量、羽绒的种类及含绒量、充绒量的指标、洗涤标识、质量等级、执行标准代号等；看产品外观、缝制质量；看辅料：一件羽绒服上，有不少辅料，如拉链、金属扣等，是否美观、光滑、松紧适宜。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">挑选羽绒服时，除了要看含绒量还要看填充物的质量(充绒量)，同型号、含绒量相同的羽绒服，填充物的充绒量越多，羽绒服保暖性越好。羽绒服外形庞大圆润，保暖性较佳。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">二按：将羽绒服放松铺平，用手按压羽绒服，随即将手松开，看羽绒服是否能很快回弹起来恢复原状。迅速回弹，恢复原状的，说明羽绒的蓬松度良好。如含绒量低，掺有一定量的毛片或粉碎毛的，回弹性就差，并感到羽绒服拎在手里有沉重感。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">三摸：用手摸捏羽绒服，测试其手感柔软程度、有无完整的小毛片等。羽毛梗应该细软，毛梗要有但不能多，如果完全没有毛梗则可能不是羽绒，但毛梗太多含绒量就少，羽绒品质和保暖性都较差。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">四拍：拍打羽绒服，看针脚处有无粉尘溢出、有无绒毛钻出。用力将羽绒服拍一拍，抖一抖，如果这时会有许多羽绒丝钻出来，则可能使用的布料防钻绒性差，或者缝纫针眼太大，这种羽绒服会愈穿愈薄，保暖性也会愈差。由于羽绒具有柔滑的特性，偶有少量的绒丝从缝线处溢出是正常的。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服不能钻绒，但又要具有一定的透气性，如羽绒服的面料、里料、胆料的透气性差，一是穿着过程中的水汽不易散发，引起潮湿而感到不舒适、不保暖。二是洗涤后不易晒干，以上二个因素都会使羽绒在受潮的条件下产生不同程度的变质，或滋生微生物，并散发臭味。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">五嗅：鼻子贴近羽绒服细嗅一嗅，再与正常羽绒服装对比，检查有无腥味或异味，避免买到味重刺鼻的商品。但由于羽绒是从动物身上采集的，有淡淡的羽绒气味是正常的。</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">转载请注明出处，雅迪儿制衣：</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (229, 20, '内容导读：羽毛：覆盖在鸭、鹅体表的质轻而韧、具有弹性和防水性的、由表皮角质化所生长成的一种结构，称为羽或羽毛。\r\n羽绒：生在雏鸭、鹅的体表或成鸭、鹅的正羽基部的、羽枝柔软、羽小枝细长、不成瓣状的绒毛。</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">什么是羽毛、羽绒？配图说明</span></h1>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽毛：覆盖在鸭、鹅体表的质轻而韧、具有弹性和防水性的、由表皮角质化所生长成的一种结构，称为羽或羽毛。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120614/1_120614162008_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="羽毛结构图" src="/uploads/allimg/c130513/13D435955D520-22461.jpg" width="214" height="220" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒：生在雏鸭、鹅的体表或成鸭、鹅的正羽基部的、羽枝柔软、羽小枝细长、不成瓣状的绒毛。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120614/1_120614162057_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="" src="/uploads/allimg/c130513/13D4359563Y40-3H31.jpg" width="274" height="254" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">鹅、鸭绒的外形特征大体相同，在一般情况下，鹅绒的绒朵比鸭绒大，但大型鸭的绒朵也很大，而仔鹅的绒朵又小于一般的鸭绒。所以，绒朵大小，不是区分鹅、鸭绒的显著标志。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: center"><img style="cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120614/1_120614162138_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="割绒鸭绒" src="/uploads/allimg/c130513/13D43595HJZ-41296.jpg" width="637" height="270" /><br />\r\n鹅绒和鸭绒（右）</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (230, 20, '内容导读：羽毛羽绒的基本知识有哪些？羽绒是一种动物性蛋白质，比棉花（纤维素纤维）保温性高，且羽绒球状纤维上密布千万个三角形的细小气孔，能随气温变化而收缩膨胀，产生调温功能，可吸收人体散发流动的热气，隔绝外界冷空气的入侵。羽绒特性\r\n\r\n羽绒良好的服用性能是由羽绒独特的轻柔保暖和吸湿放湿的良好性能所决定的。\r\n\r\n保暖性好。立体状结构，能够保有大量空气，可以阻绝冷空气；</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽毛羽绒的基本知识有哪些</span></h1>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒是一种动物性蛋白质，比棉花（纤维素纤维）保温性高，且羽绒球状纤维上密布千万个三角形的细小气孔，能随气温变化而收缩膨胀，产生调温功能，可吸收人体散发流动的热气，隔绝外界冷空气的入侵。</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒特性</span></strong><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒良好的服用性能是由羽绒独特的轻柔保暖和吸湿放湿的良好性能所决定的。</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">保暖性好。立体状结构，能够保有大量空气，可以阻绝冷空气；</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">良好的调温功能。羽绒上的节点，能够随气温变化而收缩膨胀，产生调温功能；</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">优良的吸湿放湿性。羽绒结构复杂，表面积大，结点吸收水分后，能够很快散发，而且羽绒本身含有油脂，不沾湿。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">雅迪儿制衣专业定做北京羽绒服,是一家具有多年制作<strong></strong>,庆洋羽绒服加工厂承接外贸羽绒服订单，详情请咨询雅迪儿制衣。客户专线：400-600-1689<br />\r\n<strong></strong>专题：</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (231, 20, '内容导读：不同功能羽绒服的面料成分及羽绒服内填充物不同，羽绒服是羽绒行业主要的产品。羽绒是由绒（Down）和羽（Feather）构成的。庆洋厂家就羽绒服都有哪些成分？羽绒服保暖性能作下介绍。</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服都有哪些成分？羽绒服保暖性介绍&mdash;&mdash;【羽绒服成分】</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">不同功能<strong></strong>成分及羽绒服内填充物不同，</span><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">是羽绒行业主要的产品。羽绒是由绒（Down）和羽（Feather）构成的。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">庆洋厂家就</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服都有哪些成分？羽绒服保暖性能作下介绍。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;　</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">高档次羽绒服一般选用90%以上的白鹅绒或90%以上的白鸭绒，真正的90%以上的羽绒服保暖性强，蓬松度又高，羽绒服穿着又轻，又舒适。一般使用含绒量90%羽绒，充绒量230g</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">～</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">320g(根据商品尺寸）的羽绒服才适应在北方零下20度<span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">～</span>零下30度左右的环境。羽绒服如果用手摸，如果摸得出很多毛杆的话绝对不是90%羽绒，如果羽绒服用手压这然后把手放开的话，90%羽绒很快就蓬松起来回复原来状态，如果用手压一下然后放手羽绒服还是扁扁的样子的话！可能您购买的羽绒服没有达到90%羽绒，充绒量也不够，保暖性也很低。90%白鹅绒羽绒服(1张)绒（Down）是由不含毛杆的羽毛，在其羽枝上长出的许多簇细丝，通过绒上的细丝相互交错形成了稳定的热保护层。因此，绒是羽绒保暖的主要材料。每一盎司的羽绒大约有2百万根细丝。较好品质的绒细丝较长，形成的绒朵也相应较大。羽（Feather）是鸭或鹅的背部和尾部的带羽杆的小羽毛，也有长羽毛打碎后形成的，羽的含量不能太高，但因为它有提高羽绒蓬松度的作用，因此必须含有一定的比例。将羽绒经过洗涤、干燥、分级等工艺处理以后，被制成羽绒服。成为冬季御寒服饰。&nbsp;羽绒服具有防寒性好、轻柔蓬松、洗涤方便、物美价廉、而且绿色纯天然等优点，所以消费者对羽绒服的需求越来越旺盛，使羽绒服市场的发展空间依然很大。（来源：）</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (232, 20, '内容导读：羽绒服面料种类也不少，一般以高密度尼丝纺、春亚纺为主，羽绒服填充物有鸭绒、鹅绒或羽绒，一般以鸭绒为普遍，羽绒服的材料主要是羽绒和涂层织物。下面详细介绍下羽绒服面料的羽绒和涂层织物。</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">羽绒服面料的羽绒和涂层织物的介绍&mdash;&mdash;【羽绒服面料】</span></h1>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">种类也不少，一般以</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">高密度尼丝纺、春亚纺为主</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，</span><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">有鸭绒、鹅绒或羽绒，一般以鸭绒为普遍，</span><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">的材料主要是羽绒和涂层织物。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">下面详细介绍下</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">羽绒服面料的羽绒和涂层织物。</span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">◆</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">羽绒：小羽片和绒子(也称朵绒)的混合物。前者称羽，后者称绒。多用鸭和鹅的毛，经选洗分离出小羽片和绒子用作羽绒服的絮料。羽绒有灰白两种，白者为佳。羽绒服的质量与充绒量和含绒量有关。充绒量指一件羽绒服絮进的羽绒重量，用克表示，一般为250克左右,充绒量少,保暖性差;含绒量指羽绒中绒子的含量,用百分比表示，一般含绒量为50～80%。含绒量高，则质量好。因绒子能使人体热量不易散失,且手感柔软,但当受压和遇湿后不易及时鼓起，而小羽片此时则能使衣服蓬松鼓起以保持衣内有较多的空气，有助保暖,但小羽片多了,热量易流散，且有毛梗感。所以羽绒服面料厂家在使用时绒子和小羽片必须兼收并蓄，比例得当。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">◆</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">涂层织物</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">：</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">选用经纬纱高密的丝绸、棉布、棉涤等织物，经羽绒服面料厂家轧压处理，使经纬纱之间的空隙缩小，再涂以高分子浆料，使之与织物形成交链的透明皮膜覆盖层，以封闭织物经纬间隙。有的在涂层浆料内加入氟磷树脂或有机硅类防水剂，使织物具有防露绒、防渗水的性能。20世纪80年代已有不经涂层的特制超高密织物，同样能起到防露绒、防渗水和透气的作用。用于羽绒服的织物分硬性、软性二类。涤府、涤卡、棉布属硬性类，穿着平整;真丝塔府绸、尼丝纺属软性类，穿着柔软舒适。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">雅迪儿制衣：</p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `dede_addonarticle` VALUES (233, 20, '内容导读：羽绒服面料都有哪些分类？常见的羽绒服面料类型有防水型涂层（覆膜）面料，高密度防泼水面料，普通梭织面料加防绒布，那几种面料都有哪些优缺点？</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服面料都有哪些分类？羽绒服面料优缺点介绍&mdash;&mdash;【羽绒服面料】</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">都有哪些分类？</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">常见的<strong></strong>面料类型有</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">防水型涂层（覆膜）面料</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">高密度防泼水面料</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">普通梭织面料加防绒布</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，那几种面料都有哪些优缺点？</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、防水型涂层（覆膜）面料&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">这类面料有点类似于冲锋衣面料，具有防水透湿的性能，一般用于高山专业型羽绒服。但不同的是，面料整体会比冲锋衣面料更加轻薄柔软一些。另外因为羽绒服一般在寒冷环境下使用，针对的主要以冰雪的固态水的</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">融水</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">为主，因此面料耐水压的要求不会像冲锋衣那么高，而且大多数采用</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">防水面料</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">制成的羽绒服是不用压胶的。另一点需要注意的是，某些低廉的羽绒服为了防止漏绒而使用不透气的</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">涂层面料</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，如果仅仅是日常穿着，可以勉强考虑。代表面料：dryloft、PROO-TEC&nbsp;LM&nbsp;等等。&nbsp;　　</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、高</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">密度</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">防泼水面料&nbsp;　</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">本身织物的密度就很高，一般在290T以上。然后再通过高温融合表层织物以减小织物空隙的后期处理工艺，提高防绒性。面料的轻薄、柔软程度是所有羽绒服面料里面最高的，同时具有防风、防泼水、透气性能。这类面料是羽绒服和羽绒睡袋使用最广法的面料，但后期处理工艺的高低对于面料的防绒性影响很大。代表面料：pertex、soft-b等等。&nbsp;　　</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、普通</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">梭织面料</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">加防绒布&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一般采用密度较低的</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">尼龙</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">或者涤纶，在制作羽绒服的时候，在面料里侧添加防绒布，可以起到防绒的作用，防绒性能不错。缺点是，防绒布影响了羽绒服的柔软度，并起增加了整衣的重量。最重要的是如果使用的是低劣防绒布的话，羽绒服的透气性会大大降低，而且在洗涤之后，防绒布容易破损或结块。另外一种方式是作防绒处理，其工艺是在面料里层刷上一层防绒胶，面料手感很差，并且不透气。代表面料：很多、但不会是知名面料厂商。&nbsp;　</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">三种类型面料性能对比：★★★表示该项性能最好；防水型涂层（覆膜）面料假设面料透气性是符合要求的，普通梭织面料里面的防绒布也假设是符合规范的；此表仅为基本参考值，实际情况根据三个类型里各面料的工艺会有较大的出入。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">面料类型&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sp