dding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">如何分辨羽绒服新款</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">羽绒服的优劣？</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">1、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">一般正规的厂家，会在产品上注明填充物，比如龙鸟Tibet羽绒服的填充物为&ldquo;250克600FP&nbsp;90%白鸭绒&rdquo;，指的是该羽绒服填充了250克600蓬松度的含绒量为90%的白鸭绒。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">2</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">、通过手捏来直观的感觉，一般毛梗手感不明显说明含绒量高，反之则含绒量低。但是要注意如果感觉不到什么毛梗，则很有可能使用飞丝填充的羽绒服。飞丝是在羽绒加工过程中从羽毛上脱落的无梗短丝毛，保暖性差，而且也没什么蓬松度，洗后结块。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">3</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">、观察羽绒的回弹性：羽绒服的回弹性在一定程度上体现了羽绒的蓬松度，可以把的羽绒服压平后展开，看羽绒服能否在较短的时间内回复原状。　&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">如何分辨羽绒服新款</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">羽绒服</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">面料</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">的</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">优劣?</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">1</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">、选择采用知名面料厂商制作的羽绒服，比如dryloft、PROO-TEC&nbsp;LM、pertex、SOFT-B等等，安全系数较高。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; 