-repeat: initial initial; ">雅迪儿制衣网：有兴趣的朋友可以进入相应网站报名，预祝此次职业装博览会成功！</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''litpic''}/uploads/allimg/c130506/13CS1562SG0-ON7_lit.jpg{/dede:field}\r\n');
