nt-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">起关键点在于<strong>校服面料</strong>的选择，</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">在生产成衣的过程中,面料是最关键的,应该从根本上杜绝</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">面料</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">PH值和超标和甲醛等有害化学物质的危坏!&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">在生产厂行家选择面料后一定要经过检验部门去检测，确认合格后，方可大批量生产。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''litpic''}{/dede:field}\r\n');
