: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">校服没有一个统一的标准，许多小企业或小工厂只要有能力生产。他们绝不会放弃赚钱机会，</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">其结果直接导致了校服质量不一</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">，</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">危害学生身体健康的问题</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p 