style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">的</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">装备。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一件<strong></strong>决定了西服的版型效果，在定做高档西装时，一定要选择知名度高的西装面料，什么牌子西装面料算是好的面料呢？他们都有什么特色呢？庆洋西装定制厂家为推荐一些知名的品牌面料及他们的面料特色。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span style="font-size: medium">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">男人的着装魅力源于西装面料的选择&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Marzoni玛佐尼</span></strong></p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">面料特色：高级定制广泛使用的意大利面料品牌，亚麻系列包括100%亚麻、棉和莱卡混纺、竹纤维等成分，其中一些条纹款式非常优雅，很适合中国江南晚春到仲夏的气候。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">也</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">是世界最顶级的面料之一，精选顶级面料原料，名贵的绢丝、马海毛，羊驼毛，山羊绒等精制而成。</span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">男人的着装魅力源于西装面料的选择&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Ermenegildo&nbsp;Zegna杰尼亚</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">面料特色：植根于意大利传统，又充满时尚气息，它的高品质在于对细节与舒适的追求以及对每一位顾客特质的充分考虑，是欧洲皇室贵族乃至世界范围内商界巨贾，达官绅士最推崇的品牌。&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">男人的着装魅力源于西装面料的选择&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Garavani&nbsp;VALENTINO格拉瓦尼.华伦天奴&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">面料特色：源于意大利，是全球高级男装定制和高级成衣最顶级的奢侈品品牌。华伦天奴代表的是一种宫廷式的奢华，高调之中却隐藏深邃的冷静，从60年代以来一直都是意大利的国宝级品牌。&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">男人的着装魅力源于西装面料的选择&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">Harrisons哈里森</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">面料特色：具有悬垂性好、耐穿性好、可裁剪性好、款式经典等特点。Harrisons面料款式低调、保守、庄重、沉稳，手感柔中有刚，滑中有糯，弹性足，外观挺括气派，富有质感，是具有代表性的英国面料。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span style="font-size: medium">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">以上是庆洋推荐的一些比较优质的品牌面料，最终要的还是坚持以自己的方式，近乎苛刻的要求严格把关西服面料采购，以确保成衣品质，使得男士西服在公众心中树立了标志性的旗帜，当然这些也成为各大定制西服品牌的创业宗旨。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">雅迪儿制衣官网：（）</span></p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: medium">\r\n<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''pubdate''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''litpic''}{/dede:field}\r\n');
INSERT INTO `dede_co_htmls` VALUES (324, 4, 0, ' 西装面料都有哪些种类？最全的西装面料种类大揭秘——【西装面料】 ', '', 'http://www.bjqingyang.com/mianliaozhishi/xifu/16730.html', 1368435877, 1, 1, '{dede:field name=''keywords''}西装面料,西服面料种类{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''description''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''title''}西装面料都有哪些种类？最全的西装面料种类大揭秘——【西装面料】{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''writer''}雅迪儿制衣{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''source''}雅迪儿制衣网{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''body''}内容导读：西装面料都有哪些种类？每个种类下又有哪些分类，庆洋为您揭开最全的西装面料种类及各自特点。\r\n一、西装面料种类——混纺织品\r\n　　1、涤毛花呢。其中涤纶55%，羊毛45%，质地较厚实，手感丰满，强力高，牢度好，挺括、抗皱性好。宜做秋冬服装；\r\n　　2、凉爽呢。其中涤纶55%、羊毛45%，料薄，但坚牢耐穿，具有爽、滑、挺、防皱、防缩、易洗快干等特点。宜做春夏服装，不宜做冬季服装</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">西装面料都有哪些种类？最全的西装面料种类大揭秘&mdash;&mdash;【西装面料】</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"></span></span></strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">都有哪些种类？每个种类下又有哪些分类，庆洋<strong></strong>为您揭开最全的西装面料种类及各自特点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一、西装面料种类&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">混纺织品</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　1、涤毛花呢。其中涤纶55%，羊毛45%，质地较厚实，手感丰满，强力高，牢度好，挺括、抗皱性好。宜做秋冬服装；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　2、凉爽呢。其中涤纶55%、羊毛45%，料薄，但坚牢耐穿，具有爽、滑、挺、防皱、防缩、易洗快干等特点。宜做春夏服装，不宜做冬季服装；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　3、涤毛粘花呢。涤纶40%、羊毛30%、粘胶丝30%，呢面细洁，毛型感强，条纹清晰，挺括，牢度较好，价廉，经济实惠。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">西装面料种类&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">纯化纤织品</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　1、纯涤纶花呢。表面平滑细洁，条型清晰，手感挺、爽，易洗快干，穿久后易起毛。宜做男女春秋装；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　2、涤粘花呢(快巴)。涤纶50～65%、粘胶丝50～35%，毛型感强，手感丰满厚实，弹性较好，价廉。宜做男女春秋服装；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　3、针织纯涤纶。质地柔软，弹性好，外观丰满、挺括，易洗快干。宜做男女春秋服装。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">西装面料种类&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">全毛织品</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　1、华达呢。纱支细，呢面乎整光洁，手感滑润，丰厚而有弹性，纹路挺直饱满。宜缝制西服、中山服，女上装。缺点是经常摩擦的部位膝盖、后臀部极易起光；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　2、哔叽。纹路较宽，表面比华达呢平坦，手感软，弹性好，不及华达呢厚实、坚牢，用途同华达呢；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　3、花呢。按重量可分为薄花呢(300克以下／米)和中厚花呢(300～400克／米)。呢面光洁平整，色泽匀称，弹性好，花型清晰，变化繁多。宜做男女各种外套、西服上装；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　4、啥味呢。光泽自然柔和，呢面平整，表面有短细毛绒，毛感柔软。宜做春秋两用衫及西服；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　5、凡立丁。毛纱细，原料好，但密度稀，呢面光洁轻薄。手感挺滑，弹性好，色泽鲜艳耐洗。宜作夏令服装和冬季棉袄料；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6、派立司。光泽柔合，弹性好，手感爽滑，轻薄风凉，牢度不及凡立丁。最适合做夏季男女各式服装；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　7、女衣呢。纱支较细，结构较疏松，手感柔软，而富有弹性，花色多，色艳丽。常用作女春秋两用衫和棉袄面子；</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　8、直贡呢。密度大，手感厚重、柔软，表面平滑，光泽明亮，富于弹性。宜做大衣、中山服。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="color: #ff0000"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;提示：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><font face="宋体">选购</font></span></span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="font-size: medium"><font face="宋体">时，也不必拘泥于必需要纯毛的，或者高含毛的产品。选购保暖性好的秋冬季西服时，可以考虑纯毛或者高含毛的厚实面料，而春夏季西服则可以考虑聚酯纤维与人造丝这样的化纤混纺面料。</font></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp; 庆洋：</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: medium">\r\n<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''pubdate''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''litpic''}{/dede:field}\r\n');
