INSERT INTO `dede_co_htmls` VALUES (378, 4, 0, ' 羽绒服面料哪些比较好？2012时装羽绒服新看点 ', '', 'http://www.bjqingyang.com/mianliaozhishi/yurongfu/16850.html', 1368435951, 1, 1, '{dede:field name=''keywords''}羽绒服面料哪些比较好？{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''description''}{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''title''}羽绒服面料哪些比较好？2012时装羽绒服新看点{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''writer''}雅迪儿制衣{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''source''}雅迪儿制衣网{/dede:field}\r\n{dede:field name=''body''}内容导读：羽绒服面料多采用高密度的涂层织物，能保持衣内有较多的空气，保暖性能好。羽绒服常用面料是尼龙材质的，里面的填充物有鸭绒、鹅绒或羽绒等。具体羽绒服面料介绍就有庆洋羽绒厂家来告诉大家。</div>\r\n                            <div class="maincont">\r\n                            	<div style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none" class="Section0">\r\n<h1><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服面料哪些比较好？</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><strong></strong><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">多采用高密度的涂层织物，能保持衣内有较多的空气，保暖性能好</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">。</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">常用面料是尼龙材质的，里面的填充物有鸭绒、鹅绒或羽绒等。具体羽绒服面料介绍就有庆洋羽绒厂家来告诉大家。</span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><img style="width: 684px; height: 224px; cursor: pointer" onclick="window.open(''/uploads/allimg/120614/1_120614160750_1.jpg'')" border="0" alt="羽绒服面料" src="/uploads/allimg/c130513/13D43595042P-1K51.jpg" width="1000" height="289" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">羽绒服面料哪些比较好？</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">1、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">防风透气：大部分的户外羽绒服都具有一定的防风性。透气是户外服装的统一要求，但是很多驴友却往往会忽视羽绒服面料透气的重要性。一件不透气的羽绒服在高山上产生的结果往往是致命的。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">2、</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">防绒：增强羽绒面料的防绒性有三种方式，一是在基布上覆膜或者涂层，通过薄膜或涂层来防止漏绒，当然首要的前提是透气的，并且不会影响面料的轻薄和柔软程度。二是将高密度织物通过后期处理，提高织物本身的防绒性能。三是在羽绒面料里层添加一层防绒布，防绒布的好坏将直接影响整衣的品质。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">3</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">、轻薄柔软：在装备轻量化的今天，羽绒服的面料的轻薄程度将直接影响一件羽绒服的整体重量，而且柔软的面料，对于本身就臃肿的羽绒服而言，会增强羽绒服穿着的舒适度。另外一方面，轻薄柔软的面料有助于更好的发挥羽绒的蓬松度，因此保暖性也会更高。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">4</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">、防水：主要针对专业型羽绒服，在酷寒环境下直接外穿的，羽绒服的面料要直接代替冲锋衣使用。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点一</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">时装化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">时装化将成为羽绒服新款图片的主流。生活条件越好，人们对美的追求就越高。近年来天气越来越暖，各种活动场所的环境也越来越舒适，御寒已不再是人们穿羽绒服的惟一目的。从生产技术上，羽绒服已经可以做到既轻薄又保暖。所以，在人们越来越讲究美体、线条的今天，羽绒服独特的质感又是其它服装所无法相比的。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点四</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">个性化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">个性特色鲜明的新款羽绒服图片将标新立异。注重表现个性，是新时代消费者在着装方面的一大特点，羽绒服也不例外。如情侣装、母子装羽绒服将会备受消费者的青睐。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点二</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">休闲化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">在着装上，人们将更加讲究丰富多彩和随意性。休闲服装洒脱、舒适、随意、放松，体现人们享受美好生活的乐观与惬意。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2012时装羽绒服新看点三</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">运动化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">运动化</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">的新款羽绒服图片将成为新宠。随着2008年北京奥运会临近，全民体育运动将成为社会生活一大热点。体育运动升温，必将带来运动服装消费的高潮。在羽绒服诸多功能中，运动功能将更加突出，特别是适合跑步、滑雪、滑冰、冰球等所有冬季运动项目的羽绒服将备受青睐。</span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; padding-top: 1pt; mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: none; mso-border-left-alt: none" class="p0"><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">更多羽绒服动态咨询，关注雅迪儿制衣网</span><span></span><span style="font-family: ''宋体''; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="border-bottom: medium none; text-align: justify; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 1pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 4pt; padding-right: 4pt; margin-bottom